in terms of things like spectacles and

107
00:05:53.580 --> 00:05:57.330
hearing aids maybe, or modifications to the house, ramps, et cetera.

108
00:05:57.370 --> 00:05:57.920
Yeah.

109
00:05:58.640 --> 00:05:59.000
So

110
00:06:00.540 --> 00:06:03.880
to your point at the beginning, this is really just putting in place

111
00:06:04.020 --> 00:06:06.680
legislation that reflects existing practice.

112
00:06:07.756 --> 00:06:10.256
So I just wanted to give you some reassurance there.

113
00:06:10.276 --> 00:06:10.286
It's-

114
00:06:10.336 --> 00:06:13.546
Our concern is that this bill in its present form-

115
00:06:14.436 --> 00:06:14.576
Yeah

116
00:06:14.586 --> 00:06:15.676
... with the big

117
00:06:16.496 --> 00:06:20.026
list of all the family members that you're expected to go through-

118
00:06:20.296 --> 00:06:20.306
Mm-hmm

119
00:06:20.306 --> 00:06:23.026
... which includes cousins, stepkids, all that-

120
00:06:23.516 --> 00:06:23.586
Yep

121
00:06:23.676 --> 00:06:27.326
... that is an unreasonably broad list, and that's not how it

122
00:06:27.326 --> 00:06:28.536
currently is at the moment.

123
00:06:28.916 --> 00:06:31.956
Yeah. And I take your point, the wording could be a lot clearer.

124
00:06:31.986 --> 00:06:32.136
Mm.

125
00:06:32.156 --> 00:06:33.406
And we've had that feedback from-

126
00:06:33.576 --> 00:06:34.256
Yeah. So that's-

127
00:06:34.396 --> 00:06:34.606
That's definitely-

128
00:06:34.606 --> 00:06:38.416
That's our main concern is that as it is currently from the bill,

129
00:06:38.626 --> 00:06:40.426
taken directly from the bill-

130
00:06:41.146 --> 00:06:41.146
Yep

131
00:06:41.146 --> 00:06:45.136
... that wording is c- cause of huge alarm

132
00:06:45.176 --> 00:06:46.386
in the community. And

133
00:06:48.476 --> 00:06:49.796
that's not the community's fault.

134
00:06:49.836 --> 00:06:52.856
That's taken directly from their own government's legislation.

135
00:06:53.636 --> 00:06:55.376
Yeah. And we've heard that feedback.

136
00:06:55.396 --> 00:06:56.295
So that's our concern.

137
