01:09:15.605 --> 01:09:19.324
Build this bill on the foundations we already know work so

1257
01:09:19.364 --> 01:09:23.204
disabled people can live as valued and contributing citizens,

1258
01:09:23.784 --> 01:09:27.664
families are genuine partners, and future generations inherit a

1259
01:09:27.764 --> 01:09:30.804
disability support system that upholds rights,

1260
01:09:31.105 --> 01:09:33.445
